      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage slaw</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>chilli relish </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>chilli mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1644331239040-x200.jpg",
