      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and then slice in half</p><p>Press the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>basa</strong> into the <strong>Cajun-style seasoning </strong>firmly to evenly coat all over</p>",
