    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa halves</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until the basa is cooked through – this is your <strong>Cajun-style basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
